                                       "Dato for første utplassering"@no ,
                                       "Data da primeira implantação"@pt ,
                                       "Data primei desfășurări"@ro ;
                        rdfs:comment "Date of the first deployment of an instrument, platform, or infrastructure."@en ,
                                     "Date du premier déploiement d’un instrument, d’une plateforme ou d’une infrastructure."@fr .


