OSO:hasEDMO
    rdfs:comment "Αυτή η ιδιότητα συνδέει έναν Οργανισμό με το αναγνωριστικό EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@el ,
                 "This property links an Organisation to its EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations) identifier."@en ,
                 "Esta propiedad vincula una Organización con su identificador EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@es ,
                 "Cette propriété relie une organisation à son identifiant EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@fr ,
                 "Questa proprietà collega un'Organizzazione al suo identificatore EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@it ,
                 "Denne egenskapen kobler en organisasjon til dens EDMO-identifikator (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@no ,
                 "Esta propriedade liga uma Organização ao seu identificador EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@pt ,
                 "Această proprietate leagă o organizație de identificatorul său EDMO (European Directory of Marine Organisations)."@ro ;
    rdfs:label "έχει EDMO"@el ,
               "has an EDMO"@en ,
               "tiene un EDMO"@es ,
               "a un EDMO"@fr ,
               "ha un EDMO"@it ,
               "har en EDMO"@no ,
               "tem um EDMO"@pt ,
               "are un EDMO"@ro ;
    skos:prefLabel "έχει EDMO"@el ,
                   "has an EDMO"@en ,
                   "tiene un EDMO"@es ,
                   "a un EDMO"@fr ,
                   "ha un EDMO"@it ,
                   "har en EDMO"@no ,
                   "tem um EDMO"@pt ,
                   "are un EDMO"@ro .

